title: Uriah Heep - Shady Boston (Live 2-CD) 1976 ak320
description:
Uriah Heep - Shady Boston (Live 2-CD) 1976 ak320

I picked this up and later I looked for some description LOL. There are shysters and trolls selling this from 20 to 50 USD all over the place LOL. Just one more Good reason why I share
and am glad that others do as well. And why all who grab should seed. Much cheaper than the going prices.

Live at Orpheum Theatre, Boston, MA. USA 6th May 1976

Master recording taped by Dan Lampinski 

Disc 1 (46:35)
1. Intro. 2. Devil's Daughter 3. Stealin' 4. Shady Lady 5. Make A Little Love
6. One Way Or Another 7. The Wizard 8. July Morning
 
Disc 2 (50:39)
1. Midnight 2. Easy Livin' 3. Gypsy 4. Improvisation 5. Sweet Lorraine 6. Bass Solo
7. Sweet Lorraine(reprise) 8. Bird Of Prey 9. Love Machine 10. Look At Yourself


David Byron - Vocal / Mick Box - Guitar Ken / Hensley - Keyboards & Guitar / John Wetton - Bass / Lee Kerslake - Drums
